history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.2.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.2.0-01 /bin/sh -c mkdir -p /opt   && curl --fail --silent --location --retry 3   --header "Cookie: oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie; "   http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}u${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR}-b${JAVA_VERSION_BUILD}/server-jre-${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}u${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR}-linux-x64.tar.gz   | gunzip   | tar -x -C /opt   && ln -s /opt/jdk1.${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}.0_${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR} ${JAVA_HOME}

history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.2.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.2.0-01 /bin/sh -c mkdir -p ${NEXUS_HOME}   && curl --fail --silent --location --retry 3     ${NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL}   | gunzip   | tar x -C ${NEXUS_HOME} --strip-components=1 nexus-${NEXUS_VERSION}   && chown -R root:root ${NEXUS_HOME}

history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.2.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.2.0-01 /bin/sh -c useradd -r -u 200 -m -c "nexus role account" -d ${NEXUS_DATA} -s /bin/false nexus   && mkdir -p ${NEXUS_DATA}/etc ${NEXUS_DATA}/log ${NEXUS_DATA}/tmp ${SONATYPE_WORK}   && ln -s ${NEXUS_DATA} ${SONATYPE_WORK}/nexus3   && chown -R nexus:nexus ${NEXUS_DATA}

history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.3.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.3.0-01 /bin/sh -c yum install -y   curl tar   && yum clean all

history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.3.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.3.0-01 /bin/sh -c mkdir -p /opt   && curl --fail --silent --location --retry 3   --header "Cookie: oraclelicense=accept-securebackup-cookie; "   http://download.oracle.com/otn-pub/java/jdk/${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}u${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR}-b${JAVA_VERSION_BUILD}/server-jre-${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}u${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR}-linux-x64.tar.gz   | gunzip   | tar -x -C /opt   && ln -s /opt/jdk1.${JAVA_VERSION_MAJOR}.0_${JAVA_VERSION_MINOR} ${JAVA_HOME}

history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.3.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.3.0-01 /bin/sh -c mkdir -p ${NEXUS_HOME}   && curl --fail --silent --location --retry 3     ${NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL}   | gunzip   | tar x -C ${NEXUS_HOME} --strip-components=1 nexus-${NEXUS_VERSION}   && chown -R root:root ${NEXUS_HOME}

history.author: Sonatype <cloud-ops@sonatype.com>
history.created_by: |2 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.3.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_VERSION=3.3.0-01 /bin/sh -c useradd -r -u 200 -m -c "nexus role account" -d ${NEXUS_DATA} -s /bin/false nexus   && mkdir -p ${NEXUS_DATA}/etc ${NEXUS_DATA}/log ${NEXUS_DATA}/tmp ${SONATYPE_WORK}   && ln -s ${NEXUS_DATA} ${SONATYPE_WORK}/nexus3   && chown -R nexus:nexus ${NEXUS_DATA}

|5 NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_SHA256_HASH=6b186ec3514dbadf89a92d560b1c9098fd3caa1d2d5e7f5402fcf61a3d6418fb NEXUS_DOWNLOAD_URL=https://download.sonatype.com/nexus/3/nexus-3.30.0-01-unix.tar.gz NEXUS_REPOSITORY_MANAGER_COOKBOOK_URL=https://github.com/sonatype/chef-nexus-repository-manager/releases/download/release-0.5.20190212-155606.d1afdfe/chef-nexus-repository-manager.tar.gz NEXUS_REPOSITORY_MANAGER_COOKBOOK_VERSION=release-0.5.20190212-155606.d1afdfe NEXUS_VERSION=3.30.0-01 /bin/sh -c yum install -y --disableplugin=subscription-manager hostname procps     && curl -L https://www.getchef.com/chef/install.sh | bash -s -- -v 14.12.9     && /opt/chef/embedded/bin/erb /var/chef/solo.json.erb > /var/chef/solo.json     && chef-solo        --recipe-url ${NEXUS_REPOSITORY_MANAGER_COOKBOOK_URL}        --json-attributes /var/chef/solo.json     && rpm -qa *chef* | xargs rpm -e     && rm -rf /etc/chef     && rm -rf /opt/chefdk     && rm -rf /var/cache/yum     && rm -rf /var/chef     && yum clean all
